{"tid":2279122,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]觀塘boardgame音樂廢柴谷招人","createTime":"2020-11-09T14:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T01:53:10.000Z","uid":46610,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64f4c5719cbc23b14f90f81cf036b79b4ecdf3f1","tid":2279122,"uid":46610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"舊post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2232896/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2232896/page/1</a><br />\n大約過左一個月時間 事情發展唔係我控制到既野 <br />\n原本淨係想搵幾個朋友 得閒上黎我個私兜玩下吹下水<br />\n而家個谷都有一定人數 變做一星期有regular(六/日)一次活動 <br />\n個場個局都比第1次好左好多(都唔好期望同出面有得比)<br />\n歡迎未接觸過board game既你加入 因為我自己都係新手<br />\n暫時晏晝都係玩partygame為主 你黎到唔會怕唔識玩<br />\n夜晚先有機會出現難少少既驚<br />\n歡迎毒撚既你加入 因為我都係毒撚 玩驚毒又怕what<br />\n輕鬆玩 識下朋友 我淨係負責提供場地同暫時10零隻驚 都一定夠玩一日既<br />\n(利申可以玩足一日三國殺)<br />\n另外一樣都係想搵人夾下歌 我係彈結他(唔勁) 純粹想試下2個一彈一唱係點樣先<br />\n由於小弟毒得制 如果你想一入黎就話夾歌我應該做唔到 <br />\n可以係到玩幾次認識下先再慢慢黎 <br />\n我使命係拯救毒撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DyfORVQ_K_BuMytzo32Srw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDyfORVQ_K_BuMytzo32Srw&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=4132b4ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DyfORVQ_K_BuMytzo32Srw</a><br />\n<strong>有興趣先好入</strong> 入完冇興既都quit谷啦 唔好等我以為有好多人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d9106cd6e170d4a510b683a3c597412e892b3d","tid":2279122,"uid":46610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:04:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DyfORVQ_K_ChV76KReOfdg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDyfORVQ_K_ChV76KReOfdg&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=4167ddc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DyfORVQ_K_ChV76KReOfdg</a><br />\n輕輕一推 入黎要答一條問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人識玩coup"},{"pid":"81f38a979675